<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٢٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">أَبِي وَائِلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1339">حُذَيْفَةَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«أَتَى النَّبِيُّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="special">ﷺ</span> سُبَاطَةَ قَوْمٍ فَبَالَ قَائِمًا، ثُمَّ دَعَا بِمَاءٍ فَجِئْتُهُ بِمَاءٍ فَتَوَضَّأَ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>